<h3>Email Address</h3><p>It is important to make sure you email address is valid and is working.&nbsp; The system will email order notifications and other information to this email address.&nbsp; If the system sends and email to a customer, the from address will be this one so all your customers have to do is hit their Reply button to respond to you or email you a question.&nbsp; If this address is not working or is invalid, you will not receive notfications and your customers will receive errors when trying to respond to you.</p>




